{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fighting has always been in your blood. From petty street fights, to Ranger school and finally to the 5th Special Forces Group, fighting was the only thing that made sense. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Years after leaving the service you find yourself\u00a0 living in the heart of London, carving a path in the competitive world of Mixed Martial Arts. Not the life you had envisioned, but comfortable nonetheless. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When a sudden tragedy thrusts you back into the past you'd left behind and the only link a young woman has to the rest of the world you find yourself with a new outlook on life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you navigate the dangerous world of professional sports, while managing to keep yourself and those around you safe and sane? Or will you finally succumb to the pressure around you and break? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You won't be alone on this journey however, meet the lovely group of ladies who will join you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Viridiana &quot;Vi&quot; Davis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338660/extras/Viridiana_Ad.png?t=1736825060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A young woman from your youth. With her world collapsing around her can you provide the comfort she needs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Amrit Swain</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338660/extras/Amrit_Ad.png?t=1736825060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A genius kickboxer and your personal protege.\u00a0 Will you be coaching her in more than just the art of fighting?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Elspeth Adair</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338660/extras/Elspeth_Ad.png?t=1736825060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The prodigal scion of an old and prestigious bloodline. Will you prove worthy to discover this beautiful (and somewhat intimidating) woman's secrets?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kanako &quot;Kana&quot; Taiaroa</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338660/extras/Kana_Ad.png?t=1736825060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hailing from beautiful New Zealand this young woman has fled the only life she's ever known.\u00a0 Will you help return her to the path she's always belonged on?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ines Auclair</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338660/extras/Ines_Ad.png?t=1736825060\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Young, vibrant and a bit of a hopeless romantic. Perhaps she's exactly what you need in your life? Depends on your tolerance for TTRPGs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unbroken is a story-focused visual novel experience.  No grinding, minigames, or free-roam. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Book One is an introductory installment that contains the first half of the story: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Parts 1 through 7</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">17,580 story renders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a096 Animations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A replay theater to revisit lewd scenes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736825060","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338660/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736825060","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a